---
import LightningIcon from "../../icons/LightningIcon.astro";
import PaletteIcon from "../../icons/PaletteIcon.astro";
import QuickIcon from "../../icons/QuickIcon.astro";
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
import NextIcon from "../../icons/Next.astro";
import BookIcon from "../../icons/BookIcon.astro";
import SpaceIcon from "../../icons/SpaceIcon.astro";
import AddIcon from "../../icons/AddIcon.astro";
import TipsIcon from "../../icons/TipsIcon.astro";
---

<DocsLayout>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <section
      class="text-center mb-12 p-8 bg-linear-to-r from-cyan-950/40 to-blue-950/40 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <QuickIcon class="size-10 text-cyan-400" />
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-3 bg-linear-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text"
        >
          Quick Start Guide
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-white">
        Get up and running with Astro and Tailwind CSS in minutes
      </p>
    </section>

    <section
      class="mb-12 p-6 bg-black/70 rounded-lg border border-white/20"
    >
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-4">What You'll Learn</h2>
      <p class="text-white mb-4">
        In this guide, we'll walk you through the essential steps to start
        building with Astro and Tailwind CSS. This assumes you already have
        Node.js installed on your system.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-6">
        <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-950/10 rounded-lg border border-cyan-500/50 hover:bg-cyan-950/30 hover:transition-colors hover:duration-500">
          <div class="flex gap-1">
            <LightningIcon class="text-yellow-400"/>
            <h3 class="text-cyan-300 font-bold mb-2">Fast Setup</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-white">
            Get your project running in under 5 minutes
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-blue-950/20 rounded-lg border border-blue-500/50 hover:bg-blue-950/30 hover:transition-colors hover:duration-500">
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <PaletteIcon class="size-6 text-cyan-400"/>
            <h3 class="text-blue-300 font-bold mb-2">Styling</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-white">
            Start building beautiful UIs with Tailwind CSS
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-4 bg-purple-950/20 rounded-lg border border-purple-500/50  hover:bg-purple-950/30 hover:transition-colors hover:duration-500"
        >
          <div class="flex gap-1">
            <NextIcon class="size-6 text-white"/>
            <h3 class="text-purple-300 font-bold mb-2">Next Steps</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-white">Learn where to go from here</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-black/70 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/20 hover:border-cyan-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group"
      >
        <div
          class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          1
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-2">
            Create Your Project
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white mb-4">
            Use the Astro create command to scaffold a new project:
          </p>
          <div
            class="bg-white/10 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto"
          >
            <code>npm create astro@latest my-astro-app</code>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-4 bg-blue-950/30 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 rounded-lg"
          >
            <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">
              ðŸ’¡ When prompted, select TypeScript and confirm the setup options.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-black/70 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/20 hover:border-cyan-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group"
      >
        <div
          class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          2
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-2">Navigate & Install</h2>
          <p class="text-white mb-4">
            Move into your project directory and install dependencies:
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-cyan-300 mb-2">Navigate to project:</p>
              <div
                class="bg-white/10 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto"
              >
                <code>cd my-astro-app</code>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-cyan-300 mb-2">Install Tailwind CSS:</p>
              <div
                class="bg-white/10 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto"
              >
                <code>npx astro add tailwind</code>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-black/70 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/20 hover:border-cyan-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group"
      >
        <div
          class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          3
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Start Building</h2>
          <p class="text-white mb-4">Start the development server:</p>
          <div
            class="bg-white/10 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto"
          >
            <code>npm run dev</code>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white mt-4">
            Open <code class="bg-purple-500/10 font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300"
              >http://localhost:4321</code
            > in your browser to see your new project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 bg-black/70 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/20 hover:border-cyan-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-500/10 group"
      >
        <div
          class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-2xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
        >
          4
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-2">
            Create Your First Component
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white mb-4">
            Create a new Astro component in <code
              class="bg-purple-500/10 font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300"
              >src/components/Welcome.astro</code
            >:
          </p>
          <div
            class="bg-white/10 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-cyan-500 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto"
          >
            <div
              class="bg-white/5 text-cyan-300 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-700 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto"
            >
              <pre>---
// Component script
const message = "Welcome to Astro!";
---

&lt;div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 rounded-lg"&gt;
  &lt;h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white"&gt;&#123;message&#125;&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;p class="text-white/80 mt-2"&gt;Start building awesome things&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-4 bg-green-950/30 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-4 rounded-lg"
          >
            <p class="text-green-200 text-sm">
              âœ“ Astro combines HTML, CSS, and JavaScript syntax. You can use
              Tailwind classes directly in your components!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="mb-12 p-6 bg-black/70 rounded-lg border border-white/10"
    >
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-6">Common Next Steps</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div
          class="p-4 bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-lg border border-cyan-500/30 hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all"
        >
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <BookIcon class="size-6 text-white" />
            <h3 class="text-cyan-300 font-bold mb-2">Learn Astro</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm mb-3">
            Explore templates, layouts, and component composition in the
            official documentation.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://docs.astro.build"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 text-sm font-medium" 
          >
            Visit Astro Docs â†’
          </a>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-4 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg border border-blue-500/30 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all"
        >
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <PaletteIcon class="size-6 text-white"/>
            <h3 class="text-blue-300 font-bold mb-2">Customize Tailwind</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm mb-3">
            Modify colors, typography, and spacing in your tailwind.config.mjs
            file.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 text-sm font-medium"
          >
            Tailwind Documentation â†’
          </a>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-4 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-lg border border-purple-500/30 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all"
        >
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <SpaceIcon class="size-6 text-white"/>
            <h3 class="text-purple-300 font-bold mb-2">Deploy Your Site</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm mb-3">
            Learn how to deploy your Astro project to production platforms.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/deploy/"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 text-sm font-medium"
          >
            Deployment Guide â†’
          </a>
        </div>
        <div
          class="p-4 bg-pink-500/10 rounded-lg border border-pink-500/30 hover:border-pink-500/50 transition-all"
        >
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <AddIcon class="size-6 text-white"/>
            <h3 class="text-pink-300 font-bold mb-2">Add Integrations</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm mb-3">
            Enhance your project with React, Vue, or other framework
            integrations.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/integrations-guide/"
            target="_blank"
            class="text-pink-400 hover:text-pink-300 text-sm font-medium"
          >
            Integration Guide â†’
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-lg border border-cyan-500/20"
    >
      <div class="flex gap-1">
        <TipsIcon class="size-9 text-cyan-400" />
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Pro Tips</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">â†’</span>
          <span class="text-white"
            ><strong class="text-yellow-400">Use .astro components</strong> for static
            content and HTML-based features</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">â†’</span>
          <span class="text-white"
            ><strong class="text-yellow-400">Leverage Tailwind utilities</strong> for rapid
            UI development without writing CSS</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">â†’</span>
          <span class="text-white"
            ><strong class="text-yellow-400">Optimize for speed</strong> - Astro ships
            zero JavaScript by default, keeping your sites lightning-fast</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">â†’</span>
          <span class="text-white"
            ><strong class="text-yellow-400">Check the project structure</strong> - Organize
            components and pages logically for scalability</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
